Some Examples:
## Reasons for creation of this library.


## Examples

### Simple Get
```php
require ("PhCURL.php");
$curl = new PhCURL();

//Some useful settings:
$curl->setConnectTimeout(2)
     ->loadCommonSettings();

$curl->setUrl("http://www.google.com")
     ->GET();

$htmlCode = $curl->getData();
$curl->close();
```
### Ouput Info
You can fetch all info with `$curl->getInfo()` or by calling single methods. I.e.
```

echo <<<EOF
<pre>
Url: {$curl->getUrl()}
Code: {$curl->getHttpCode()}
DocumentTime: {$curl->getFileTime()}
Total Time: {$curl->getTotalTime()}
Time NameLookup {$curl->getNameLookupTime()}
Connect Time: {$curl->getConnectTime()}
Pretransfer Time: {$curl->getPretransferTime()}
StartTransfer Time: {$curl->getStartTransferTime()}
Number of Redirects: {$curl->getRedirectCount()}
Redirect Time:{$curl->getRedirectTime()}
Uploaded Bytes:{$curl->getSizeUpload()}
Download Bytes:{$curl->getSizeDownload()}
Speed DOwnload:{$curl->getSpeedDownload()}
Speed Upload:{$curl->getSpeedUpload()}
Header SIze:{$curl->getHeaderSize()}
-----
Header Out: \n{$curl->getHeaderOut()}
-----
Request Size: {$curl->getRequestSize()}
Content Length: {$curl->getContentLengthDownload()}
Content Type: {$curl->getContentType()}
----
EOF;
```
